ActCanada Transportation Act
Financial Administration Act
SubjectProgram to strengthen the efficiency and resilience of National Trade Corridors Fund
PrecisOrder Approving that the Minister of Transport ENTER into FUNDING AGREEMENTS with eligible recipients under the NATIONAL TRADE CORRIDORS FUND, a program to strengthen the efficiency and resilience of national trade corridors, for a maximum amount of $500,000,000 per project.
